1
00:00:57,440 --> 00:00:58,240
Detective

2
00:00:58,480 --> 00:00:59,840
Please, save my daughter

3
00:01:00,480 --> 00:01:02,080
The Wang family wants to kill her

4
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:04,400
Don't worry, I'll save her for sure

5
00:01:09,800 --> 00:01:10,600
Who is it

6
00:01:36,360 --> 00:01:38,440
Since Shuang'er died

7
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:40,600
My son has been losing his mind

8
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:44,800
We invited Master Cao to collect Shuang'er's bones

9
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:47,400
To ward off disaster for my son

10
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:57,280
My son Sanming was harmed by this woman

11
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:01,760
Hurry and collect the bones

12
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:06,200
Don't let this woman harm our Wang family again

13
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:10,920
Drive out evil, break the ground

14
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:16,000
So-called bone collecting

15
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:19,360
Means taking up remains buried for years

16
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:22,680
Then rebury them in a new blessed grave site

17
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:26,240
That way, disaster can be dispelled and blessings sought

18
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:28,040
So the family may prosper

19
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:30,520
Hold up the umbrella

20
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:38,280
Smash the tombstone

21
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,520
Open the coffin

22
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:43,960
All of you Wangs deserve to die

23
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:45,480
You all deserve to die

24
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:47,520
Shuang'er

25
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,640
Master

26
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:16,120
A right hand bone is missing

27
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,600
A sign of great calamity

28
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:22,800
Take him away, now

29
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:24,480
Take the young master away, now, quickly

30
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:26,160
None of you Wangs will die well

31
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:30,240
Even as a ghost, I won't spare you

32
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:32,760
With one right hand bone missing

33
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:36,080
Can one be added to avoid disaster

34
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,200
No

35
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:40,720
Using another dead person's hand bone instead

36
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:43,080
Will bring a wronged spirit's deadly claim

37
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:44,720
And make the calamity even worse

38
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:02,720
Master, snow in June signals a great injustice

39
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:03,840
Shut up

40
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:09,880
Master

41
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:25,720
Since Master Cao says dead bones won't do

42
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,840
Then living bones should do, right

43
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:30,280
You cut off an innocent person's arm

44
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:32,560
It goes against heaven and human morals

45
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:34,840
You will surely suffer Divine retribution

46
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:37,400
I can't collect these bones

47
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:44,520
I'm telling you, in Nanwan Town

48
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:48,000
I am heaven

49
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:51,920
I'd like to see what heaven cannot tolerate

50
00:04:52,280 --> 00:04:55,280
You must collect these bones

51
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,200
Otherwise

52
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:15,760
Shuang'er, the Wang family's vengeful spirit, will kill again

53
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:21,640
A third severed-hand case strikes Nanwan Town

54
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:33,120
Another severed hand

55
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:36,520
A missing right hand bone is a dire omen

56
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:22,440
Ow, ow, ow, it's numb, numb, numb

57
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,800
Zheng Yu

58
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,320
It's been three years

59
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:29,840
I was only joking with you

60
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,200
Why'd you hit so hard

61
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:33,160
So you do know it's been three years

62
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:35,000
I told you to come find me, and you never did

63
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,800
I was busy

64
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,560
Busy with what, exactly

65
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:40,440
How's the information I asked you to check

66
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,840
Do you even need to ask

67
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:44,040
After all, I am Nanwan Town's one and only

68
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,120
great swindler

69
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,200
great detective

70
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,600
Hand over the file

71
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:56,640
The three severed-hand victims were all tied to the Wangs

72
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:59,560
The first was a Wang family thug

73
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:01,400
The second delivered goods to the Wang family

74
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:03,320
The third was a mailman

75
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:04,880
He wasn't one of the Wangs

76
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:08,640
But he and Shuang'er, the Wang family's daughter-in-law, were from the same hometown

77
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:13,800
Oh, right, Zheng Yu

78
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:16,240
Why are you so certain

79
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:19,240
This severed-hand case is tied to your master's affair

80
00:07:32,280 --> 00:07:34,400
Three years ago, the Wang bone collecting failed

81
00:07:34,840 --> 00:07:36,960
And then Master disappeared

82
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:38,760
He only left this behind

83
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:42,280
Th-this is

84
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:44,080
Master's right hand bone

85
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:52,960
Back then, Master left me this letter

86
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,320
Telling me to leave Nanwan Town

87
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:57,040
And never come back again

88
00:07:58,680 --> 00:07:59,760
In these three years

89
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:03,600
Many Vengeful Spirit's Claim cases happened in Nanwan Town

90
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:05,880
The times are in turmoil now

91
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:09,120
The police station is already in utter chaos

92
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:11,120
They have no time to deal with the Wang family

93
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:13,560
The Wang family has dominated Nanwan Town for years

94
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,320
Aren't you afraid

95
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:17,320
Master died a wrongful death for no reason

96
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:19,960
And there are countless wronged souls in Nanwan Town

97
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:24,640
This time back, I will uncover the truth

98
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,480
And restore peace to Nanwan Town

99
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,520
Come quick, come look

100
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:30,800
A wedding procession, a wedding procession

101
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:39,120
Master Wang is marrying again

102
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:41,520
Her elder sister was the last wife

103
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,800
The sister died, so he married the younger one

104
00:08:44,040 --> 00:08:44,960
Come to think of it

105
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:47,920
In the Wang family, a concubine dies every three years

106
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:50,840
That is damned eerie

107
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:01,680
Xu Nan

108
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,600
Dearest

109
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:12,600
No... wh-what is going on?

110
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:14,480
How did Dearest become Madam Wang?

111
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:17,440
No, what is going on?

112
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:26,840
My sister died right here

113
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:29,680
For my sister

114
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:32,600
I gave up almost everything

115
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:36,560
My future, my freedom

116
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:40,600
Even the man I loved

117
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:43,200
That bone collecting boy has been missing for three years

118
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:44,480
You should forget him soon

119
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,520
Now the Wang family has come with a proposal again

120
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:47,840
I have already accepted the betrothal gifts

121
00:09:47,920 --> 00:09:50,120
This time, you must marry

122
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:09,840
What is happening?

123
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,040
Th-this is...

124
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:15,200
What is it? Wh-what is this?

125
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:22,880
Give me back my right hand

126
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:25,720
I died so miserably

127
00:10:27,680 --> 00:10:30,160
Give me back my right hand

128
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:39,080
Master, what did you see?

129
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:41,440
It is Shuang'er's wronged spirit here to claim a life

130
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:45,360
Everyone, quiet down, quiet down

131
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:49,280
Someone is pretending to be ghosts here

132
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,800
Everyone, do not panic, do not panic

133
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:55,520
Steward, go see what is going on

134
00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:02,480
Shuang'er is claiming a life

135
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:06,200
The Wang family truly has some unspeakable secret
